title: Insurgency v2.2.7.3
description:
Take to the streets for intense close quarters combat, 
where a team's survival depends upon securing crucial strongholds and destroying enemy supply in this multiplayer 
and cooperative Source Engine based experience. 
The follow-up game to the award-winning Source mod, 
Insurgency is highly competitive and unforgivingly lethal, striking a balance between one-life gameplay and prolonged action
